{"tid":1238321,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好見藍絲分化就打飛機","createTime":"2019-06-17T18:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:23:19.000Z","uid":258170,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5e45d4c0abd9721d51ce74c6e5abbdffd295c1f1","tid":1238321,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:40:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><em>其實今日見禮義廉又叫啲老人登記做票倉</em></span><br />\n啱先見到有巴打留咗呢句，覺得要推出嚟，俾大家多番啲警覺性。<br />\n藍絲依家雖然分化，但係後果其實比我哋分化冇咁嚴重。<br />\n因為佢哋係睇建制頭嘅。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">建制可以快速由上而下咁籠絡民意</span></strong>。出返啲著數氹下佢哋，講返幾句似是而非嘅理論，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲就會回頭</span></strong>，乖乖排隊撐港共。<br />\n就算班官整咗幾大個大頭佛都好，記住<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">建制頭頭係中央</span></strong>。統戰，唔係吹水。呢頭林奠盧仔condom 一鍋粥，呢頭統戰戰隊就已經出動。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲嚟講，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">建制分化只會係短期效果，我哋唔可以因為呢樣嘢自high</span></span><br />\n<br />\n繼續俾壓力班廢柴，繼續打鍵戰延長藍絲分化嘅時間，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">堅持撤回收例撤回收例撤回收例</span></span>，先係我輩當為！"},{"pid":"0428e43bc147d73c0ab341ed80f2dece5941536e","tid":1238321,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:41:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7d3d4dd010b5dbdd6fd38aa4bc0570ef6126bec","tid":1238321,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf58f1b270706b51dbab480ab5107540f22fe224","tid":1238321,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:43:47.000Z","msg":"頂，打錯字tim<br />\n<br />\n唔好搞錯重心<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅持撤回修例</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅持撤回修例</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅持撤回修例</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a925a539eb62d1fcccd9453c6414d2ec5647b932